name: Spring Strapless Polkadot Rockabilly Pencil Dress with Hand Embroidered Sparrows
description: This vintage inspired strapless dress has a sweetheart neckline. It is done in 100% cotton fabric in white with little baby blue polka dots all over. This dress has a darted pencil skirt with a kick pleat. There are two hand embroidered sparrows at the bottom hem. It has a invisible back zipper and the top is fully lined. Measurements Bust: 35 inches Waist: up to 32 inches Hip: up to 34 inches Length: 39 inches from base of neck This dress is a size Medium. Size S-2XL are available and are made to order, please allow 1-2 weeks for production and shipping.
